name: gdu v5.31.0
body:
## What's Changed
* feat: relative path ignore support by @s0up4200 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/398
* feat: Add support showing size of absent git-annex'ed files by @stv0g in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/404
* fix: ctrl_z corruption #253 by @yurenchen000 in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/406
* fix: item count for --show-item-count by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/416
* fix: automatically run non-interactive when related flag set by @dundee in https://github.com/dundee/gdu/pull/418
